2011-09-13T09:52:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/hotai-motor-co-august-sales-rise-96-67-table-2207-tt.html
HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in August rose 96.67% to NT$6,050,833,000 from NT$3,076,669,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales           6,050,833        3,076,669   
YOY%              96.67%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           54,060,962       51,980,732  
YOY%              4.00%  
=================================================================
 